if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('LS_Orderletian')
and type = 'U')
drop table LS_Orderletian
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: LS_Orderletian */
/*==============================================================*/
create table LS_Orderletian (
OrderID int identity,
Buyer nvarchar(30) null,
telephone nvarchar(30) null,
phone nvarchar(30) null,
zip nvarchar(30) null,
address nvarchar(300) null,
shopID int null,
firstimport int null,
ImportTime datetime null,
Fee decimal(4,2) null,
totilMoney decimal(4,2) null,
SKU1 nvarchar(50) null,
SKU2 nvarchar(50) null,
Num int null,
OrderNub nvarchar(100) null,
SysOrderNub nvarchar(100) null,
beizhu nvarchar(200) null,
lasttime datetime null,
constraint PK_LS_ORDERLETIAN primary key (OrderID)
)
go
